    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "gotcha. so on one hand you have the regulators saying they're monopolies, and on the other you have the companies saying they're just innovating. given how much these companies actually dominate the market, do you think the current antitrust laws are actually capable of keeping up, or are they pretty much outdated for the digital age?",
